page.title: 06A TYPICAL DAY IN MY LIFE
page.content:
A typical day of my life on Wednesday June l9th l985. I woke up, got washed and dressed then I had some toast and a drink. I usually have to spill something down me, this time it was my coke all down my clean shirt, so I had to get changed, by this time I was already late for school so I had to quickly jump into the car and go and pick Leanne and Julie up. When we got to school we went to our classroom and had a General Knowledge test.
In Maths and French it was just like a normal lesson and after that it was break. I had a packet of crisps and then talked to my friends until the bell rang, then it was CDT, after that my friends and I went up to the chip shop and had sausage and chips.
